menuconfig MCDT
	bool "MCDT Hardware Support"
	help
	  MCDT is a Hardware module that can be used to transfer data between AP
	  and DSP, normally we use it transfer audio data.
	  Say Y if your platform supports hardware MCDT.

if MCDT
config MCDT_DRV
	bool "MCDT driver"
	help
	  MCDT_DRV is the driver of MCDT.
	  Say Y if you want support this driver.
endif
